@node "menu_transfer_upload" "Upload                 "
@{u} action @{uu}

Selected protocol is XPr 2.001

Pops up file requster where you can select files to upload, currently selected
protocol is used. You can hold tab key if you want to select more than one
file but then protocol must support batch file send. 

Selected protocol is External

Will just start external program after fiddling with serial, full explanation
about serial @{"here" link "help_xp_type" 0}.
@endnode

@node "menu_transfer_upload_using_lis" "Upload using list"
@{u} action @{uu}

Same as upload but files to be uploaded are taken from @{"Upload list" link "help_fi" 0}, note that
upload list is flushed immediately. With external protocol this just starts it
after flushing upload list.
@endnode

@node "menu_transfer_download" "Download"
@{u} action @{uu}

Selected protocol is XPr 2.001

Will just start XPr protocol in download mode, currently you cannot use
protocols which request user to type download name. Those shouldn't be used
anyway as they are crappy.

Selected protocol is External

Will just start external program after fiddling with serial, full explanation
about serial @{"here" link "help_xp_type" 0}.
@endnode

@node "menu_transfer_rv_active" "Active"
@{u} global @{uu}

When this is checked then review is active, unchecking this will free all
memory used by review.
@endnode

@node "menu_transfer_rv_view" "View"
@{u} action @{uu}

This will open review window.
@endnode

@node "menu_transfer_rv_size" "Size"
@{u} global @{uu}

How many lines to collect review buffer before starting deleting oldest lines.
@endnode

